{"tha-ap320:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap320:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap320:0.3":"Tiramsiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap320:1.1":"“Kesarim abhijatamva, ","tha-ap320:1.2":"aggikkhandhamva pabbate; ","tha-ap320:1.3":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap320:1.4":"siddhattham pabbatantare. ","tha-ap320:2.1":"Suriyassa ca alokam, ","tha-ap320:2.2":"candalokam tatheva ca; ","tha-ap320:2.3":"Buddhalokanca disvana, ","tha-ap320:2.4":"vitti me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap320:3.1":"Tayo aloke disvana, ","tha-ap320:3.2":"sambuddham savakuttamam; ","tha-ap320:3.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap320:3.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap320:4.1":"Tayo hi alokakara, ","tha-ap320:4.2":"loke lokatamonuda; ","tha-ap320:4.3":"Cando ca suriyo capi, ","tha-ap320:4.4":"buddho ca lokanayako. ","tha-ap320:5.1":"Opammam upadassetva, ","tha-ap320:5.2":"kittito me mahamuni; ","tha-ap320:5.3":"Buddhassa vannam kittetva, ","tha-ap320:5.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap320:6.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap320:6.2":"yam buddhamabhikittayim; ","tha-ap320:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap320:6.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap320:7.1":"Ekasatthimhito kappe, ","tha-ap320:7.2":"eko nanadharo ahu; ","tha-ap320:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap320:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap320:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap320:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap320:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap320:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tiramsiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap320:10.1":"Tiramsiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}